\par \pard \s6\qj\keepn\nowidctlpar Blood pressure dead weight testers - Methods and means of verification
\par \pard\plain \qj\nowidctlpar \f15\fs26 {\b\i 
\par }\pard \qj\nowidctlpar\tx360 {\b 
